What was the problem with compareToIgnoreCase API ?

compareToIgnoreCase method compares two strings. If we are comparing two versions such as "2.2.1" with "2.11.1" this api fails because digit after first dot are 2 and 1 in this case 2 is grater than 1 hence result will be "2.2.1" > "2.11.1" which is not expected. Hence compareVersions() api is added to perform version comparison.
